      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## Changes\n\n### Bug Fixes\n- **Image title attribute now emitted in Storage Format output** — `titleAttr` was computed in `confluenceStorageRender.image()` but never appended to the `<ac:image>` tag, so image titles in markdown (`![alt](url \"title\")`) were silently dropped. Fixed for both attachment and external URL paths.\n\n### Code Quality\n- Handle `navigator.clipboard.writeText` rejection with a user-visible Notice instead of swallowing the error\n- Cache `editor.getSelection()` call\n- Remove commented-out dead code and redundant `PluginSettingTab.hide()` override\n\n### Tooling\n- Added ESLint (flat config + `eslint-plugin-obsidianmd` recommended)\n- Upgraded TypeScript 4.7 → 5.7, esbuild 0.17 → 0.25\n- Modernized release workflow (replaced deprecated `actions/create-release@v1`, `upload-release-asset@v1`, `::set-output`, Node 14 → 20)\n- CI now runs lint + tests on Node 18/20/22\n\n### Quality\n- 130/130 tests pass\n- 0 lint errors",
